{"service_name": "Organisation and Job Design", "service_id": "7137301224709085", "company_name": "Health HR UK Ltd", "page_content": "<main id=\"content\" role=\"main\">\n <div class=\"grid-row\">\n  <div class=\"column-two-thirds\">\n   <header class=\"page-heading-smaller\">\n    <p class=\"context\">\n     Health HR UK Ltd\n    </p>\n    <h1>\n     Organisation and Job Design\n    </h1>\n   </header>\n  </div>\n </div>\n <div class=\"grid-row\">\n  <div class=\"column-two-thirds\">\n   <p class=\"service-summary-lede\">\n    We can design a new organisational structure and hierarchy for clients linked to their target operating model, developing job specifications and role profiles to enable job enrichment, job rotation, or job enlargement. This involves determining the necessary governance, required reporting lines, and subsequent activity associated with the organisational changes.\n   </p>\n   <h2 class=\"service-summary-heading\">\n    Features\n   </h2>\n   <ul class=\"service-summary-features-and-benefits\">\n    <li>\n     Can assist with re-structuring, mergers, or down-sizing of companies\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Can help evaluate jobs including JEGS and HAYES\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Can perform skills gap analysis or skills audits\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Can deliver performance management systems\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Can manage personal development planning\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Can manage career paths\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n   <h2 class=\"service-summary-heading\">\n    Benefits\n   </h2>\n   <ul class=\"service-summary-features-and-benefits\">\n    <li>\n     Can undertake skills assessment and skills mapping\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Can manage redeployment, redundancy and exit schemes\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Can manage consultation with trade unions\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"column-one-third\">\n   <div id=\"meta\">\n    <h2 class=\"visuallyhidden\">\n     Pricing\n    </h2>\n    <p class=\"price\">\n     \u00a3500 per person per day\n    </p>\n    <ul class=\"price-caveats\">\n     <li>\n      Excluding VAT\n     </li>\n     <li>\n      Minimum contract period: Other\n     </li>\n    </ul>\n    <h2 class=\"visuallyhidden\">\n     Service documents\n    </h2>\n    <ul class=\"document-list\">\n     <li class=\"document-list-item\">\n      <a class=\"document-link-with-icon\" href=\"https://assets.digitalmarketplace.service.gov.uk/g-cloud-7/documents/700226/7137301224709085-pricing-document-2015-10-02-1203.pdf\">\n       <span class=\"document-icon\">\n        pdf\n        <span>\n         document:\n        </span>\n       </span>\n       Pricing\n      </a>\n     </li>\n     <li class=\"document-list-item\">\n      <a class=\"document-link-with-icon\" href=\"https://assets.digitalmarketplace.service.gov.uk/g-cloud-7/documents/700226/7137301224709085-sfia-rate-card-2015-10-02-1204.pdf\">\n       <span class=\"document-icon\">\n        pdf\n        <span>\n         document:\n        </span>\n       </span>\n       SFIA rate card\n      </a>\n     </li>\n     <li class=\"document-list-item\">\n      <a class=\"document-link-with-icon\" href=\"https://assets.digitalmarketplace.service.gov.uk/g-cloud-7/documents/700226/7137301224709085-service-definition-document-2015-10-02-1203.pdf\">\n       <span class=\"document-icon\">\n        pdf\n        <span>\n         document:\n        </span>\n       </span>\n       Service definition\n      </a>\n     </li>\n     <li class=\"document-list-item\">\n      <a class=\"document-link-with-icon\" href=\"https://assets.digitalmarketplace.service.gov.uk/g-cloud-7/documents/700226/7137301224709085-terms-and-conditions-2015-10-02-1203.pdf\">\n       <span class=\"document-icon\">\n        pdf\n        <span>\n         document:\n        </span>\n       </span>\n       Terms and conditions\n      </a>\n     </li>\n    </ul>\n    <h2 class=\"sidebar-heading\">\n     Framework\n    </h2>\n    <div class=\"external-link-default\">\n     <